{"tid":1474173,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】以現鈔表達決心和訴求的香港市民","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:12:55.000Z","uid":193565,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4c913c63760208b0f1d1fc91d8473c1bfe91e7","tid":1474173,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"歷時兩個月的反送中運動，使港共暴政完完全全暴露於市民眼中，警暴、官商鄉黑合作等令人髮指的行為已經使香港市民對政府完全失去信心，更有消息指中共已經竊取香港的外匯儲備，匯豐高層於中國平安成為大股東後相繼離職，可見中共之惡手已伸延至香港銀行體系，使港人對其信心大降。<br />\n<br />\n觀乎近日中國軍隊於深圳邊境集結，香港市民有理由相信中共可能會以軍隊對港進行鎮壓，屆時人人惶恐、外資撤離。另外，港元一年期權於昨晚已跌穿7.85，證明市場預期港元1年內將會與美元脫鈎，聯繫匯款崩潰，港元勢成廢紙，若要自保，必先將大部份資產轉換成美元或其他可靠外幣，才能保值。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今早再有消息傳出中共望將香港變成直轄市，取消一國兩制，取消港元在港的合法地位，以人民幣進行交易，企圖盡數竊取港人的外匯儲備，升斗市民若要防範魔鬼暴政帶來的資產損失，只能在此時將港元轉換成外匯，手持現鈔，才是真財富，屆時樓價大跌，磚頭亦不保值。<br />\n<br />\n經本人一晚的收集，加上【傾閪咩？】巴打的貼文(<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472715</a>) ，已有超過百位市民率先將存款提出，港元等值以億計，部分人已開始兌換外幣，本人在此呼籲市民，若要保值，必先提現、兌美金或其他可靠外幣，香港市民的財產不能被共產黨蠶食。市民應以現鈔表態，透過減少銀行現金流，堅決反對中共在港的一切所作所為，並對暴政表示強烈譴責，防止手上資產成為垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8.16撳錢換美金</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjYu9Hw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjYu9Hw.jpg&h=a2882c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXCsbVT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXCsbVT.jpg&h=8094b54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5KNWuM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5KNWuM.jpg&h=fbc8770d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHXcn9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHXcn9M.jpg&h=34771dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVAQUgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVAQUgs.jpg&h=11c3b8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLEeBuN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLEeBuN.jpg&h=6d8445bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vn5dR28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvn5dR28.jpg&h=348fc882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下為整合前原圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/10usZILGZnF97BGcoI2CWPazn_QD9jnpg?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F10usZILGZnF97BGcoI2CWPazn_QD9jnpg%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=3bc866bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/10usZILGZnF97BGcoI2CWPazn_QD9jnpg?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"980bdde8806c2cd6ab8a4c6da7550ee95cc2970c","tid":1474173,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303e51ac6dd1e96070f8940ec5f5f64ce6506435","tid":1474173,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fc1d2a271b969402a3d5ebcc321b3fda63edbcf","tid":1474173,"uid":74432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"民陣8.18遊行<br />\n日期：8月18日（星期日）<br />\n集合時間：下午3時<br />\n起點：維園遊行至中環遮打花園"},{"pid":"1e88118950bff6ac9e3a0901b58cf42b0d436e58","tid":1474173,"uid":184952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"794664f007d7ebddb3e00a03bf9965aa54b07aa0","tid":1474173,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebe96215528d750d1cb88cd878a110728384d477","tid":1474173,"uid":248326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:42:10.000Z","msg